#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/removal_strategies/closest_location.rst:83
msgid ""
"To check the on-hand stock at each storage location, open "
"the :guilabel:`Locations` report by clicking :menuselection:`Inventory app --"
"> Reporting --> Locations`. Filter by :guilabel:`On Hand`, as well as "
