#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:35
msgid ""
"All other fields in this section are identical on the shipping method forms "
"for each shipping carrier. See :doc:`third-party shippers "
"<third_party_shipper>` for standard configuration instructions."
msgstr ""
"Tutti gli altri campi in questa sezione sono identici nei moduli dei metodi "
"di spedizione per ciascun corriere. Consultare :doc:`corrieri terzi "
"<third_party_shipper>` per le istruzioni di configurazione standard."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/dhl_credentials.rst:40
