"standard)."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:190
msgid ""
"international shipping (e.g. use :doc:`three-step delivery <../"
"daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>` to prepare documents for customs)"
msgstr ""
"spedizione internazionale (ad es. usa :doc:`consegna in tre passaggi <../"
"daily_operations/delivery_three_steps>` per preparare i documenti per la "
