#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:192
msgid ""
"in-store pickup or home delivery: ship from the central warehouse, or pick "
"from the store's stock, depending on customer selection."
msgstr ""
"ritiro in negozio o consegna a domicilio: spedisci dal magazzino centrale o "
"preleva dallo stock del negozio, a seconda della selezione del cliente."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:195
msgid ""
"To set up routes, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> "
"Routes`. Click :guilabel:`New`, or select the desired route."
msgstr ""
"Per impostare i percorsi, andare in :menuselection:`Magazzino --> "
