"il percorso desiderato."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:198
msgid ""
"On the route form, in the :guilabel:`Applicable On` section, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Shipping Methods` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Nel modulo del percorso, nella sezione :guilabel:`Applicabile a`, spunta la "
"casella :guilabel:`Metodi di spedizione`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:204
msgid "Routes form with the Shipping Methods checkbox selected."
msgstr "Modulo dei percorsi con la casella Metodi di spedizione selezionata."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:204
msgid "Routes form with the :guilabel:`Shipping Method` checkbox ticked."
msgstr ""
"Modulo dei percorsi con la casella :guilabel:`Metodo di spedizione` spuntata."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method.rst:206
msgid ""
"Then, go to :menuselection:`Inventory --> Configuration --> Delivery "
"Methods`, and select the desired shipping method."
msgstr ""
"Quindi, andare in :menuselection:`Magazzino --> Configurazione --> Metodi di "
