"amministratore <../../../../general/users/access_rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/warehouses_storage/reporting/moves_history.rst:14
msgid ""
"To access the moves history report, go to :menuselection:`Inventory app --> "
